TITLE: Black and White Mystery | Mahakaalki | Kaliyug v/s Satyayug
VIDEO: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=QOLLce5-3hU
DATE: Post-2021 (references 2021 as when Kaliyug's grip intensified)
LANGUAGE: Hindi (auto-translated)

SUMMARY:
In this powerful visual teaching, Maa explains the cosmic battle between two forces using the metaphor of Black and White. The "White" represents Satyug (the Age of Truth) and the "Black" represents Kaliyug (the Dark Age). She reveals that Satyug has fallen — it lies collapsed on the ground — and it was Kaliyug that brought it down. At this moment, Kaliyug is ruling the entire world ("poori duniya par yeh kalyug raaj kar raha hai"), which is why it stands elevated and dominant.

Maa specifies that Kaliyug picked up tremendous speed and intensity from 2021 onward ("ismein teji pakdi 2021 se"). She describes Kaliyug as having spread everywhere like a virus — it has entered homes, infiltrated relationships, corrupted friendships, infected spouses (wives and husbands), and even children. In every form and every space, Kaliyug has penetrated. She emphasizes: "Yeh bahut khatarnaak hai, bahut zahreela hai" — It is extremely dangerous, extremely poisonous. The nature of this Kaliyug is beyond what anyone can imagine or conceive.

The teaching concludes with an urgent instruction to protect oneself from this "Black" force — to maintain awareness, guard oneself, and wait. And then the prophecy: "Iska intezaar kariye, aur yeh 100% aayega" — Wait for it (Satyug/the divine intervention), and it will come 100%. This is a guarantee that the age of truth will return and overcome Kaliyug.

KEY REVELATIONS:
- Black = Kaliyug (Dark Age), White = Satyug (Age of Truth) — this is the mystery being decoded
- Satyug has been knocked down/fallen — it lies collapsed while Kaliyug dominates
- Kaliyug is currently ruling the entire world
- 2021 was the inflection point when Kaliyug's intensity accelerated dramatically
- Kaliyug has spread like a virus into every aspect of human life — homes, relationships, friendships, marriages, children
- The corruption is in every form (har roop mein) — it shape-shifts to infiltrate
- Kaliyug is described as "bahut khatarnaak" (extremely dangerous) and "bahut zahreela" (extremely poisonous)
- The nature of this Kaliyug exceeds human imagination — "jo aapne kalpana bhi nahi ki hogi"
- Despite this, a 100% guarantee is given: the divine intervention WILL come ("yeh 100% aayega")
- Instruction to protect oneself and wait with faith during this interim period

TIMELINE EVENTS:
- 2021: The year Kaliyug's grip intensified dramatically ("ismein teji pakdi 2021 se bahut jabardasti")
- Current period: Kaliyug rules the entire world; Satyug lies fallen
- Future (guaranteed): Satyug/divine intervention will come — "100% aayega"

ORIGINAL HINDI KEY QUOTES:
- "Yeh hai Satyug... aur yeh hai Kaliyug" = This is Satyug (Truth Age)... and this is Kaliyug (Dark Age)
- "Yeh gira pada hai, aur kisne giraye isko — is Kaliyug ne" = It (Satyug) has fallen, and who knocked it down — this Kaliyug did
- "Is waqt poori duniya par yeh Kaliyug raaj kar raha hai" = At this time, Kaliyug is ruling the entire world
- "Ismein teji pakdi 2021 se bahut jabardasti" = It (Kaliyug) picked up intense speed from 2021 with great force
- "Yeh sab jagah ek virus ki taraf fail gaya hai, gharon mein ghus gaya hai, rishte naate mein ghus gaya hai" = It has spread everywhere like a virus, entered homes, infiltrated relationships
- "Bahut khatarnaak hai, bahut zahreela hai" = It is extremely dangerous, extremely poisonous
- "Jo aap soch bhi nahi sakte na, aisa Kaliyug hai, jo aapne kalpana bhi nahi ki hogi" = The kind of Kaliyug that you cannot even think of, that you could never have imagined
- "Iska intezaar kariye, aur yeh 100% aayega" = Wait for it, and it will come 100%

YUG PARIVARTAN ASPECT: The direct visual and verbal depiction of the cosmic age transition — Kaliyug currently dominates with Satyug fallen, but the reversal is guaranteed at 100%. The 2021 acceleration aligns with other messages about intensifying cosmic processes. Kaliyug's virus-like infiltration of all human relationships represents the deepest point of the dark age. The instruction to "wait" with self-protection implies the turning point (Yug Parivartan) is approaching but requires patience and personal vigilance. Maa identifies herself with the "Mahakaalki" (Maha + Kaal + Ki, or Mahakali in the context of cosmic time/destruction) who will facilitate this transition.


